(firstQuint)Theory of Mind in Preschool Children, School Children, Youths and Adults Born Preterm or Full-term.

 Is there any difference in the development of theory of mind between preterms and full-terms? Is there a risk group of preterms to develop a deficit in theroy of mind? Four groups are tested: prescoolers (again two years later), youths and young adults.

 All participants were tested for theory of mind, executive functions, language and cognitive abilites.

